##############################################

BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ meter} = 10 \text{ decimeters} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$m1] \text{ meters} = ``] [__________]{$dm1} [`` \text{ decimeters} ``]

a. [`` [$dm2] \text{ decimeters} = ``] [__________]{$m2} [`` \text{ meters} ``]

END_PGML


